channel.title: Fallen Angel Development Team
channel.description:
[center][img]http://www.zonalibre.org/blog/elizabeta/archives/Fallen%20Angel%2014.jpg[/img][/center] [center][size=16pt]Fallen Angel Development Team[/size][/center]
Fallen Angel is a server i ran a year ago all by myself. It was a small but fun community consuming of about 30 players at the time. Now i have come back to Moparscape i am planing of creating the Fallen Angel Community all over again. I am now putting together a Development Team to create a whole new server. If you would like to apply please copy and paste the application you see below and completely fill it out. For some background on me i have been coding Java for 2 years now and have Coding and Playing Moparscape from the start. Before i was into Moparscape or even Runescape i was a strong Forums Community Member of a couple Forums. I also ran a couple of my own and i have ran more then 5 of my own servers.
Application:Please apply for one or more of the positions below Server Coders(Will receive Administrator on the server): -Dslayer40 - - - Forums/Website Creators(Will receive Administrator on the forums/website): -Dslayer40 - - - Server Testers(Will receive Moderator on the server): -Dslayer40 - - -
